CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779214266
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of making
OL,4,Cthreats to kill in Guernsey
OL,6,FA 35-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of making threats to kill in
OL,8,FGuernsey.
OL,10,FOfficers arrested him at a private
OL,11,Faddress early Sunday morning and he
OL,12,Fremains in custody.
OL,14,FPolice say they are not looking for
OL,15,Fanyone else and say there is no
OL,16,Fevidence of any risk to the public.
OL,18,FChief Officer Damian Kitchen has
OL,19,Fcriticised speculation about the
OL,20,Fincident on social media.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
