OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779214266
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of making
OL,4,Cthreats to kill in Guernsey
OL,6,FHe said: "While enquiries were
OL,7,Fongoing, a huge amount of speculation
OL,8,Ftook place on social media, some of
OL,9,Fwhich amounted to nothing more than
OL,10,Fmisinformation.
OL,12,F"I have been made aware, for example,
OL,13,Fof comments trying to link this
OL,14,Fincident and arrest to immigration
OL,15,Fissues and race. These comments are
OL,16,Fwholly inaccurate, borderline
OL,17,Fhysterical, and quite frankly
OL,18,Funacceptable.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779214266
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of making
OL,4,Cthreats to kill in Guernsey
OL,6,F"I can give the community my guarantee
OL,7,Fthat if there was ever an immediate
OL,8,Frisk to the public, we would be fast,
OL,9,Fclear and direct in putting out a
OL,10,Fwarning to ensure people could be
OL,11,Fsafe. In this instance that was not
OL,12,Fnecessary.
OL,14,F"The situation was carefully assessed
OL,15,Fand information that is not available
OL,16,Fto the public was considered, and
OL,17,Fthere was no need for that type of
OL,18,Fwarning to be issued. It would have
OL,19,Fboth caused unnecessary alarm and made
OL,20,Fthe suspect aware we were looking for
OL,21,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
