PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779214266
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of making
OL,4,Cthreats to kill in Guernsey
OL,6,FGuernsey Police added that they made a
OL,7,Fnumber of enquiries overnight to make
OL,8,Fthe arrest quickly and prevent any
OL,9,Fescalation.
OL,11,FThe force thanked members of the
OL,12,Fpublic who assisted with the
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
